{"tid":1360700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要懲罰港鐵可唔可以咁？","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T16:15:53.000Z","uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd23f9052336b260f41ed64f77b8f3cedd01638","tid":1360700,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"其實港鐵只係租九鐵既鐵路，只要九鐵同佢斷租佢利潤就會減少，咁自然港鐵高層既花紅就會少左，而且九鐵好似冇可加可減機制同埋成日買日本車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b92acbc0535bc2ddd30f1f93a6e78303bacfc2","tid":1360700,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4d101bac649968de3fddbb955b84be6d2ea1277","tid":1360700,"uid":70403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"兩年前已經冇俾過錢撘地鐵<br />\n每次都跳閘"},{"pid":"49cce7a19a56f23da1eeda8b80cb6ab2ce7453fd","tid":1360700,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/profit_ch.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Farchive%2Fcorporate%2Fch%2Finvestor%2Fprofit_ch.pdf&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9W6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=c605fb42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/profit_ch.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n根據2018港鐵年報<br />\n<br />\n香港客運業務收益（姐係你哋交嘅車錢）佔總收入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">38.3%，達82億港元</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港車站商務（舖租，廣告費）佔總收入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">27.6%，達59億港元</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兩者合共佔港鐵收入接近七成<br />\n如果大量市民唔交車費，舖頭唔夠膽租港鐵站沿線商舖，商戶抵制港鐵唔落廣告<br />\n港鐵收入必定大減"},{"pid":"8e9c79c275b2705d0b5321a082cdb2ee5dca2972","tid":1360700,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cce7a19a56f23da1eeda8b80cb6ab2ce7453fd","tid":1360700,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply